comments: Powell (LAC) legally contests Thomas' (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Claxton (BKN) cleanly deflects the ball away from Zubac (LAC) during rebounding.

Thomas (BKN) steps somewhat forward towards Leonard (LAC) and Leonard spins away from the marginal contact on the perimeter.
Claxton (BKN) legally contests Zubac's (LAC) shot near the rim.
Zubac (LAC) is retreating alongside Thomas' (BKN) path and he absorbs the marginal contact at the end of the drive.
Thomas (BKN) leaves his feet to pass and he returns to the floor prior to releasing the ball.
Powell (LAC) is already in O'Neale's (BKN) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Harris (BKN) is moving alongside Leonard's (LAC) path and marginal contact occurs as they come together during the drive.

Jackson (LAC) brings his hand towards Sumner's (BKN) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Jackson (LAC) steps forward into Sumner's (BKN) body and initiates contact that affects his shot attempt near the rim.

Claxton (BKN) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.
Harris (BKN) swipes his arm down and makes contact with Batum's (LAC) arm as he is starting his upward shooting motion.
Thomas (BKN) and Powell (LAC) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.

O'Neale (BKN) brings his arm forward and makes contact with George's (LAC) arm that affects his pass attempt.
Claxton (BKN) cleanly deflects the ball away from Batum (LAC) during rebounding.
Jackson (LAC) turns slightly towards Thomas (BKN) and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Thomas (BKN) commits a take foul on George (LAC).
Correctly called 24 second violation.
